text:
@yordis 

"I would be great if in the deployment at least I could specify which folder to actually publish to npm"

You can tell npm what folders/files to put inside a package via the [files](https://docs.npmjs.com/files/package.json#files) param. I never tried it for sub-directories, but if I got what you are aiming at this could be enough to solve the mentioned problem right?
